Module jonix.common
Package com.tectonica.jonix.common

Class JPU

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.common.JPU
  • public class JPU
extends Object
    JPU (Jonix Processing Utility) is an all-static internal utility class, assisting in run time processing of the DOM elements. Shouldn't be accessed normally by users.

    IMPORTANT: Beware editing! the auto-generated classes all rely heavily on the methods in this class

    Author:
    Zach Melamed
